{"tid":731760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家00後中小學生都講普通話 好恐怖","createTime":"2018-07-06T12:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T13:13:48.000Z","uid":82228,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8674a3884d95c3c9f0dab4494d3cf907ab440151","tid":731760,"uid":82228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"平時係街見到d著住校服嘅中小學生傾計用普通話<br />\n打字用拼音<br />\n今日出席個中學生科技公開活動<br />\nPresent個陣<br />\nd中學生用唔咸唔淡嘅廣東話讀自己學校名「香港乜乜乜中學」香港兩個字都未讀好 好L諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有勁多學生用普通話present<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有個學生試圖用廣東話回答問題，但唔識講落去，最後轉返做普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過多十年會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d8f8b321b57f726d370f473b7c6ad22115fc86","tid":731760,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:54:19.000Z","msg":"過多十年香港正式被攻陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n維護廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43155214ee0f0620dd8c9dbd2a030ca3d5c7d1c0","tid":731760,"uid":124824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 捍衛廣東話"},{"pid":"6597326ed993bc4dcfe8920d42a58c517d3b87e1","tid":731760,"uid":104513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:57:00.000Z","msg":"破壞一個地方的文化 首先就係確壞佢地既語言<br />\n<br />\n好多人都習以為常，唔好話乜救香港為自由，就算依加救到遲下都會比呢班細路敗返走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" c